{"tid":366163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇煎pan女朋友單文柔","createTime":"2017-08-19T19:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T15:52:05.000Z","uid":14730,"like":8,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1dd219ffd3b1d3c71e617646380a25fb48c109b2","tid":366163,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T19:30:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/032919_4e44dd1acacf9945913448899090a1ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F032919_4e44dd1acacf9945913448899090a1ca.jpg&h=ef1e0349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/032933_f6e65862f8a91f320c0580aaa0beef3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F032933_f6e65862f8a91f320c0580aaa0beef3f.jpg&h=a1daf6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次拍劇，陳展鵬都跟女主角傳緋聞，然而，胡定欣與鍾嘉欣都是鏡花水月；終於，今次有真桃花，跟一六年落選港姐單文柔於三月在山頂約會時，被傳媒拍下照片，二人只拋下「了解中」作回應。<br />\n<br />\n經過半年相處，開花結果了，陳展鵬接受本刊訪問時，承認跟女友感情已十分穩定，與她相處感覺很舒服，並大讚：「她是一個好女仔！」不過眼見女友被網民批判和被傳媒追訪，他大感無奈，為了保護這段戀情只好選擇低調，他還笑女友有點像思覺失調，常常覺得被人跟蹤，他說︰「因為一個新人來說，好像做什麼都被人拍攝，我覺這是給她無形的壓力。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2x17hp5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2x17hp5&d=8t2LegDHZC%2FEMu4DMNQ4jhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=c4b1a336\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2x17hp5</a>"},{"pid":"2faeb56c793e97dcfd87995f24cfed83f2fccab3","tid":366163,"uid":58866,"like":153,"dislike":1,"score":152,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T20:06:55.000Z","msg":"兩個一樣有陣柒味同亞視味"},{"pid":"a68490980f13291d21af2e6249555f79b2bb8bf7","tid":366163,"uid":84423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T20:29:32.000Z","msg":"終於認啦咩"},{"pid":"01af51dce5d8ef54a18ba139696802f5e5606d06","tid":366163,"uid":56716,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T06:36:01.000Z","msg":"好似衛蘭"},{"pid"